<h1>Prerequisites</h1>

<P>Peppy requires <a href="http://www.python.org">Python</a> and the <a
href="http://www.wxpython.org">wxPython</a> widget toolkit to operate.

<ul>
<li>Install python following <a href="http://www.python.org/download/">these
instructions</a> for your platform.

<li>Install wxpython following <a
href="http://www.wxpython.org/download.php">these instructions</a> for your
platform.
</ul>

<P>Some of the optional major modes require <a
href="http://numpy.scipy.org/">NumPy</a>, but NumPy is <strong>not</strong>
required to run peppy.

